We will utilize the previous task's equation and set the EFN to zero to get the equation for the internal growth rate (expressed as g).

$$\begin{align*}
\text{EFN}&=-\text{PM(S)}\text{b}+[\text{A}-\text{PM(S)\text{b}}]\text{g}\\[10pt]
0&=-\text{PM(S)}\text{b}+[\text{A}-\text{PM(S)\text{b}}]\text{g}\\[10pt]
\text{g}&=\dfrac{[\text{PM(S)b}]}{[\text{A-PM(S)b}]}
\end{align*}$$

The previous task's equation for computing net income will be substituted into the ROA formula, and return on assets will be expressed as follows:

$$\begin{align*}
\text{ROA}=\dfrac{\text{PS}(\text{S})}{\text{A}}
\end{align*}$$
